{
  "stem": "24268.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I couldn't believe my-- I walked in, and I saw the bedspread, what belonged to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Obviously, mom probably gave as a gift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she didn't even offer a little water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then I went to this director, which she helped my brother to go to this-- to the college, to the engineering college.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She spoke about eight languages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And with this caliber of a person, and being so intelligent and no children-- she lost her husband herself.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They'd been all directors and very famous people, and being so nice to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I came up to her-- I-- that was my second stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The rest, I didn't want to go and see no one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She didn't answer, didn't offer how are you, offer a coffee, or tea, milk, glass of something, water-- not a sound.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was very heartbroken-- disappointed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I said, that's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was-- say I will never return again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to sell the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to do anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said my-- what do I need this for?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my-- if my brother lives, let him take care of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't pay attention anymore to nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where was your brother?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Russia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he got out the same way, because of the diploma as a Pole, as a Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was General Sikorski, like I was told-- my brother told me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he heard that Polish citizens, they were gonna alight-- relieve from Siberia, he obviously-- what he had still the diploma, he showed to him as a citizen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- they got out Poland-- from Siberia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how he came to look for anyone, some relatives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was in the Jewish community, because I been.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they said they would write the names where there was survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
